            <li>Security cameras and access control</li>
            <li>Procore and cloud project platforms</li>
            <li>Video meetings and remote collaboration</li>
            <li>Equipment, sensor and environmental monitoring</li>
            <li>Emergency, backup and Starlink satellite internet</li>
          </ul>
          <img class="solution-photo" src="images/mobile-starlink.jpeg" alt="Portable satellite internet terminal mounted to a construction vehicle" loading="lazy">
