          <article><h3>Weekly</h3><p>Site surveys, installations, short construction phases and temporary offices.</p></article>
          <article class="featured"><span>POPULAR</span><h3>Monthly</h3><p>Ongoing construction, renovations and long-term temporary facilities.</p></article>
