          <p class="eyebrow">COMMON QUESTIONS</p>
          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        </div>
        <details><summary>Does the equipment arrive configured?</summary><p>Yes. Each rental package is configured and tested before delivery so your team can connect with minimal setup.</p></details>
        <details><summary>Can the service support security cameras?</summary><p>Yes. We can build systems for security cameras, monitoring devices, access control and other connected equipment.</p></details>
        <details><summary>What if one cellular carrier has weak coverage?</summary><p>Multi-carrier and bonded options can use more than one available cellular network to improve reliability.</p></details>
        <details><summary>Can Wi-Fi cover a larger construction site?</summary><p>Yes. External antennas, additional access points and wireless bridges can expand coverage across larger areas.</p></details>
      </div>
