          <p class="contact-line"><strong>Prefer to speak with someone?</strong><br>Call <a href="tel:+19177505054">(917) 750-5054</a> or email <a href="mailto:joem@gothamsound.com">joem@gothamsound.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <form class="quote-form" action="https://formsubmit.co/joem@gothamsound.com" method="POST">
